         <i> That would be</i>         
      <i> the best beer ever.</i>      

08:10.624 --> 08:13.625
         - It would be          
        the worst beer!         
            - What?             

08:13.627 --> 08:14.893
         It'll get hot.         

08:14.895 --> 08:17.195
           <i> Hey, man,</i>           
         <i> it's symbolic!</i>        

08:17.197 --> 08:18.497
             Yeah!              

08:18.499 --> 08:19.698
         And since when         
      do you know so much       

08:19.700 --> 08:21.032
       about beer anyway?       

08:24.505 --> 08:27.072
      You wanna keep that?      

08:27.074 --> 08:29.040
     - I can just take it?      
           - Mm-hmm.            

08:29.042 --> 08:31.076
      Somebody wanted you       
          to have it.           

08:46.693 --> 08:49.628
            [sighs]             

08:49.630 --> 08:51.129
      Your dad would have       
      been so proud of us       

08:51.131 --> 08:53.031
