10:53.720 --> 10:55.186
         I'm your man.          

10:58.225 --> 11:00.425
             - Ah.              
       -<i> What do you say?</i>       

11:00.427 --> 11:01.926
          Thanks, Jen.          

11:05.165 --> 11:07.098
          I also have           
        a treat for you.        

11:09.069 --> 11:10.235
         It's not much.         

11:11.004 --> 11:12.837
              Um..              

11:12.839 --> 11:14.839
    Let me see where it is.     

11:16.843 --> 11:18.410
             - Oh!              
            - Ha-ha!            

11:18.412 --> 11:20.111
        You carried that        
         the whole way?         

11:20.113 --> 11:22.047
   Do you remember this oaky    
      Cab from your 30th?       

11:22.049 --> 11:24.082
     Shut up! I would have      
   split the weight with you.   

11:24.084 --> 11:27.318
         I was tempted,         
          but I wanted          
        to surprise you!        

11:27.320 --> 11:28.286
             Ahhh!              

11:29.890 --> 11:31.790
     <i> What do you say, Mom?</i>     

11:33.360 --> 11:34.859
            [laughs]            

11:34.861 --> 11:36.761
        Thank you, Jen!         

11:36.763 --> 11:38.129
        Thank you, Jen.         

11:38.131 --> 11:40.198
       - You are welcome.       
        Let's open them.        
             - Yes.             

11:40.200 --> 11:42.300
            - Both.             
             - Yes.             

11:42.302 --> 11:45.336
            <i> - Share.</i>           
       <i> - I'm gonna share.</i>      

11:45.338 --> 11:46.738
        <i> That's how much</i>        
          <i> I love you.</i>          

11:46.740 --> 11:49.007
       - Oh, is that it?        
      - That's almost it.       

11:49.009 --> 11:50.842
              Oh!               

11:50.844 --> 11:52.110
          It's so sad.          

11:52.112 --> 11:54.412
         I should have          
         brought three.         

11:56.783 --> 11:57.782
             Ahh..              

11:57.784 --> 11:59.417
           [laughing]           

11:59.419 --> 12:02.020
        <i> No more surprise</i>       
            <i> for you.</i>           

12:04.024 --> 12:05.290
         It's so good.          

12:06.493 --> 12:07.726
             Mm-hm.             

12:07.728 --> 12:09.761
             What?              

12:09.763 --> 12:11.362
      Why are you looking       
        at me like that?        

12:11.364 --> 12:13.998
           Thank you.           

12:14.000 --> 12:15.734
    We wouldn't have made it    
      up here without you.      

12:15.736 --> 12:17.168
           [laughing]           

12:17.170 --> 12:18.837
        There's no way.         

12:21.508 --> 12:25.944
    Come on, you would have     
     done the same for me.      

12:25.946 --> 12:28.780
      If I had a husband.       

12:28.782 --> 12:30.782
        And he got sick         
           and died.            

12:44.898 --> 12:46.030
             Shit.              

12:46.533 --> 12:47.899
             What?              

12:50.804 --> 12:53.138
        I forgot to call        
        the lawyer back         
        before we left.         

12:57.043 --> 12:59.043
     I have so much to do.      

13:00.514 --> 13:02.413
      My house is a wreck.      

13:02.415 --> 13:04.315
         I haven't done         
        laundry since..         

13:07.387 --> 13:09.554
      I wish I could take       
         another week,          
    but there's just no way.    

13:12.359 --> 13:14.259
     Hey, you're not alone.     

13:14.261 --> 13:17.095
          I can help.           

13:17.097 --> 13:19.030
      - And Sam can help..      
       - Sam is a child.        

13:19.032 --> 13:20.832
          - He can --           
     -<i> He can't pay bills.</i>      

13:25.372 --> 13:27.372
      And Michael is gone.      

13:28.875 --> 13:32.343
    <i> And Sam's going to grow</i>    
     <i> up without a father..</i>     

13:32.345 --> 13:35.246
     <i> ...and that is a void</i>     
      <i> that I cannot fill.</i>      

13:37.284 --> 13:39.350
        Hey, it's okay.         

13:39.352 --> 13:41.319
         It's not okay.         
         It's not okay.         

13:41.321 --> 13:44.022
    Okay. But you don't have    
        to do everything        

13:44.024 --> 13:46.291
       and you don't have       
      to know everything.       
