13:56.837 --> 13:58.136
         I'm so scared.         

14:03.410 --> 14:07.178
         I'm not read..         
         I'm not ready.         

14:07.180 --> 14:10.849
            I'm not,            
         I'm not ready.         

14:10.851 --> 14:14.352
    <i> I'm not, I'm not ready,</i>    
    <i> I'm not. I'm not ready.</i>    

14:14.354 --> 14:17.288
    - I'm really not ready.     
          - Shh. Shh.           

14:18.992 --> 14:20.592
           [sobbing]            

14:33.306 --> 14:35.273
            So, what            
       you're sayin' is..       

14:37.410 --> 14:39.410
