14:50.490 --> 14:53.191
         - Like cancer.         
           - Oh, Jen!           

14:53.193 --> 14:56.227
           I hear it.           
    Maybe a little too soon?    

14:56.229 --> 14:57.495
     But I'm dead serious.      

14:57.497 --> 14:59.931
           [laughing]           

15:01.268 --> 15:03.601
       This is not funny.       

15:03.603 --> 15:06.437
        It's not funny,         
      but we should do it.      

15:06.439 --> 15:09.173
        We need to smoke        
     that thing right now.      

15:09.175 --> 15:11.442
       <i> No, Sam's asleep.</i>       

15:11.444 --> 15:14.012
     <i> Come on, it'll be like</i>    
           <i> old times.</i>          

15:18.151 --> 15:19.417
        Okay, let me get        
         a sweatshirt.          

15:19.419 --> 15:20.585
              Yes!              

15:23.023 --> 15:25.590
         <i> Shh, be quiet!</i>        

15:27.027 --> 15:29.694
           [giggling]           

15:29.696 --> 15:32.196
     No. No, you're wrong.      
             Cou..              

15:33.466 --> 15:36.467
       Courtney Mitchell        
         had the Jetta.         

15:36.469 --> 15:39.437
       <i> Stacy Mitchell had</i>      
      <i> the White Cabriolet.</i>     

15:39.439 --> 15:41.372
    Oh, yeah, that's right.     

15:41.374 --> 15:44.509
   She had that license plate   
      that said "Topless"       

15:44.511 --> 15:46.511
           remember?            

15:46.513 --> 15:47.712
           <i> That slut.</i>          

15:49.616 --> 15:51.115
            <i> She was.</i>           

15:51.117 --> 15:53.451
      She was such a slut.      

