         from sophomore         
           chemistry?           

16:01.962 --> 16:05.229
            - Dave?             
          - Dave! Oh.           

16:05.231 --> 16:07.699
       - David Mitchell!        
       - David Mitchell!        

16:07.701 --> 16:10.435
           [laughing]           

16:10.437 --> 16:12.670
     - I remember that boy.     
         - Oh, me too.          

16:12.672 --> 16:16.107
   You used to write his name   
         on the inside          
         of your hand.          

16:16.109 --> 16:19.210
     I know it was supposed     
        to give me dibs.        

16:19.212 --> 16:22.647
    <i> Oh, you dodged a bullet,</i>   
          <i> believe me.</i>          

16:22.649 --> 16:25.350
       You dodged a very,       
       very small bullet.       

16:25.352 --> 16:27.051
           [laughing]           

16:27.053 --> 16:28.286
              Shh!              

16:28.288 --> 16:29.420
        You're welcome.         

16:32.359 --> 16:33.358
            [coughs]            

16:35.628 --> 16:37.328
       You're gonna like        
      being single again.       

16:37.330 --> 16:39.530
     Mm-mm, it's too soon.      

