     - They have apps now!      
         - Oh, my God.          

16:43.470 --> 16:45.470
        We need to work         
      on your boundaries.       

16:48.341 --> 16:49.474
           - Really?            
             -<i> Mmm.</i>             

16:50.443 --> 16:51.609
           I'm sorry.           

16:55.615 --> 16:57.682
           [laughing]           

17:00.487 --> 17:03.621
         God, it is so          

17:03.623 --> 17:07.325
      incredible out here,      
       it's so peaceful.        

17:07.327 --> 17:09.627
            - Yeah.             
             -<i> Shh.</i>             

17:11.364 --> 17:14.165
         I wish we had          
     some fucking Cheetos.      

17:14.166 --> 17:16.434
            [laughs]            

17:18.771 --> 17:20.104
          I'm serious.          

17:21.174 --> 17:23.241
      - Oh, wait a minute.      
            - What?             

17:23.242 --> 17:24.742
            [gasps]             

