   There's one chocolate chip   
         Clif Bar left.         

17:28.281 --> 17:30.615
          - I want it.          
          - I want it.          

17:30.617 --> 17:32.150
        I'm getting it.         
       I'm gonna get it.        

17:32.152 --> 17:34.152
       I'm gonna get it.        
        I'm getting it.         

