    I want to come with you.    

17:38.291 --> 17:40.224
     <i> Sam's gonna be so mad</i>     
        <i> that we ate it.</i>        

17:40.226 --> 17:41.759
     <i> Well, life's not fair.</i>    

17:41.761 --> 17:43.428
           [laughing]           

17:44.764 --> 17:47.532
       Why are the snacks       
            so far?             

17:47.534 --> 17:49.734
       Because of bears,        
            Abigail.            

17:49.736 --> 17:52.270
   You told Sam there weren't   
    any bears up this high.     

17:52.272 --> 17:54.672
     And I'm 80% confident      
          that's true.          

17:54.674 --> 17:56.107
            Eighty?             

17:58.211 --> 17:59.343
          There it is.          

17:59.345 --> 18:01.479
           [laughing]           

18:02.282 --> 18:03.648
             Whoa!              

18:06.586 --> 18:08.486
            Come on.            

18:12.358 --> 18:13.558
              Ooh.              

18:16.663 --> 18:18.830
         Mr. Clif Bar!          

18:20.633 --> 18:23.634
         Where are you?         

18:23.636 --> 18:26.204
      Jen, I'm not seeing       
         Mr. Clif Bar.          

18:26.206 --> 18:27.805
      Here, let me see it.      
       Give me the light.       

18:30.443 --> 18:32.343
           [laughing]           

18:33.746 --> 18:34.879
          Oh, my God.           

18:36.516 --> 18:38.616
     What the hell is that?     

18:47.160 --> 18:48.392
           Let me go            
        check on Sammy.         

18:48.394 --> 18:49.560
           Yeah, go.            

18:51.231 --> 18:53.231
        [dramatic music]        

18:57.637 --> 18:58.669
             Hello?             

19:23.463 --> 19:25.463
       [music continues]        

19:34.207 --> 19:35.806
      [breathing heavily]       

20:00.867 --> 20:02.600
            - Shit!             
     - Oh, God, I'm sorry.      

