     Where did you and Jen      
         go last night?         

22:53.506 --> 22:55.072
       What do you mean?        

22:55.074 --> 22:57.675
    <i> I heard you go somewhere</i>   
         <i> and come back.</i>        

22:57.677 --> 23:00.044
        Oh, we just went        
          for a walk.           

23:00.046 --> 23:01.412
        We were talking.        

23:04.150 --> 23:05.483
           About Dad?           

23:08.855 --> 23:11.989
        About old times         
       and good memories.       

23:14.761 --> 23:16.961
        - Do you smoke?         
            - What?             

23:19.165 --> 23:20.731
       <i> No, of course not.</i>      

23:22.135 --> 23:23.534
              Why?              

23:24.404 --> 23:25.870
            Did Dad?            

23:27.874 --> 23:29.640
         Did Dad smoke?         

23:29.642 --> 23:31.442
