         Do you smoke?          

23:39.786 --> 23:40.918
            No, Mom.            

23:55.101 --> 23:56.100
              <i> Mmm.</i>             

24:00.072 --> 24:01.739
         Good morning.          

24:03.209 --> 24:04.842
      The backpack's gone.      

24:09.549 --> 24:11.816
         <i> So much for my</i>        
      <i> nice relaxing shit.</i>      

24:11.818 --> 24:14.218
       Can you be serious       
         for a second?          

24:14.220 --> 24:17.488
     Do you think there was     
        someone out here        
          last night?           

24:17.490 --> 24:20.157
         <i> It's possible.</i>        
    <i> We don't own the woods.</i>    

24:24.096 --> 24:25.963
    <i> Look, maybe somebody was</i>   
          <i> coming here</i>          

24:25.965 --> 24:29.467
    <i> to set up camp and they</i>    
     <i> left their stuff here</i>     

24:29.469 --> 24:31.168
       <i> and then they went</i>      
        <i> for a nice shit.</i>       

24:31.170 --> 24:32.636
    <i> And when they came back,</i>   
          <i> they saw us</i>          

24:32.638 --> 24:33.771
    <i> and they just moved on.</i>    

24:33.773 --> 24:35.706
     You think they saw us?     

24:35.708 --> 24:37.141
           <i> That's not</i>          
    <i> what I meant, not like..</i>   

24:37.143 --> 24:38.843
          <i> Well, yeah,</i>          
       <i> maybe they saw us</i>       

24:38.845 --> 24:40.678
    <i> but they left us alone.</i>    

24:42.949 --> 24:44.748
        <i> You're freaking</i>        
         <i> yourself out.</i>         

24:46.819 --> 24:48.652
     <i> Let's just go pack up</i>     

24:48.654 --> 24:50.588
         <i> and get going.</i>        

24:52.692 --> 24:54.892
            -<i> What?</i>             
       - It's not funny.        

24:54.894 --> 24:56.494
         [Jen laughing]         

24:58.030 --> 25:00.030
        <i> You're so pretty</i>       
      <i> when you're scared.</i>      

25:00.032 --> 25:01.999
            [laughs]            

25:03.102 --> 25:05.269
       Wait for me, wait.       

25:05.271 --> 25:07.071
         <i> Sam, you want</i>         
      <i> to put out the fire?</i>     

25:08.007 --> 25:09.106
             Okay.              

25:11.544 --> 25:12.843
         [zipper opens]         

25:19.685 --> 25:21.886
    <i> Sam, what are you doing?</i>   
             <i> Stop!</i>             

25:21.888 --> 25:24.021
        I'm putting out         
           the fire!            

25:24.022 --> 25:26.155
     <i> Not with.. Ah, this is</i>    
      <i> our drinking water.</i>      

25:26.158 --> 25:27.591
           I don't..            
         I didn't know.         

25:27.593 --> 25:29.093
              <i> Bud,</i>             
     <i> what are you thinking?</i>    

25:29.095 --> 25:30.728
         Nobody told me         
       what water to use!       

25:30.730 --> 25:32.530
     <i> We have to be careful</i>     
           <i> out here.</i>           

25:32.532 --> 25:33.831
      Why are you yelling?      

25:33.833 --> 25:37.101
        <i> This is serious!</i>       

25:37.103 --> 25:39.103
      -<i> I said I'm sorry.</i>       
     - Hey, it's all good.      

25:39.105 --> 25:41.071
          We'll just..          

25:41.073 --> 25:43.007
        We'll fill it up        
          at the lake           

25:43.009 --> 25:43.807
       and let it filter        
            tonight.            

25:43.809 --> 25:44.808
            Mmm-hm.             

25:46.546 --> 25:47.745
              Bud!              

25:47.747 --> 25:50.714
      [instrumental music]      

26:20.780 --> 26:22.780
       [music continues]        

26:27.887 --> 26:29.253
             Shit.              

26:43.736 --> 26:45.035
           [whistles]           

26:47.673 --> 26:49.173
        [birds chirping]        

26:53.379 --> 26:55.179
       [music continues]        

27:06.392 --> 27:08.292
        Watch the stick.        

27:08.294 --> 27:10.861
    Oh, my, can we -- can we    
    just stop for a second?     

27:12.832 --> 27:14.632
         What's wrong?          

27:14.634 --> 27:17.735
      I'm a little dizzy.       
            I just..            
     I think it's the sun.      

27:17.737 --> 27:19.903
     Alcohol and altitude.      

27:19.905 --> 27:22.006
      That's a bad combo.       

27:22.008 --> 27:24.208
             - Sit.             
             - Oh!              

27:28.114 --> 27:31.715
         Hey, it's that         
           guy I saw.           

27:31.717 --> 27:32.683
             What?              

27:34.820 --> 27:36.253
             <i> When?</i>             

27:36.255 --> 27:38.188
         <i> Uh, yesterday.</i>        

27:39.158 --> 27:40.791
