27:40.793 --> 27:42.226
         I don't know.          

27:43.663 --> 27:45.696
        Something wrong?        

27:45.698 --> 27:47.297
        - We found a --         
           - Nothing.           

27:50.836 --> 27:53.170
        - Found a what?         
        -<i> Nothing, bud.</i>         

27:53.172 --> 27:55.172
