    He looks like a wizard.     

28:04.884 --> 28:06.917
       <i> Where's his tent?</i>       

28:06.919 --> 28:08.919
      [instrumental music]      

28:19.899 --> 28:21.198
          Come and sit          
         with me, bud.          

28:21.200 --> 28:23.434
    Let's get a bite to eat.    

28:23.436 --> 28:25.069
        <i> I'm not hungry.</i>        

28:25.071 --> 28:27.071
           Well, come           
      sit with me anyway.       

28:27.073 --> 28:28.105
              Why?              

28:29.742 --> 28:30.808
            [sighs]             

28:30.810 --> 28:31.809
          Never mind.           

28:31.811 --> 28:33.811
        [intense music]         

28:54.800 --> 28:56.800
    He's in no hurry, is he?    

28:58.137 --> 28:59.336
          You guys are          
          being weird.          

29:02.975 --> 29:04.241
    You know what, let's go.    

29:04.243 --> 29:07.010
      Just leave this guy       
          in the dust.          

29:07.012 --> 29:08.946
     All right, come on, Sam.   

29:08.948 --> 29:11.782
       [music continues]        

