          <i> so he could</i>          
       <i> text his friends.</i>       

34:04.043 --> 34:05.609
       <i> Hey, Earth to Sam!</i>      

34:05.611 --> 34:07.611
       Are we gonna move?       

34:10.416 --> 34:13.483
         No. Why would          
          we do that?           

34:17.056 --> 34:18.655
    I'm sick of that house.     

34:18.657 --> 34:20.489
       <i> You're sick of it?</i>      

34:20.492 --> 34:22.492
     <i> Bud, that's our home,</i>     
           <i> where all</i>           
       <i> our memories are.</i>       

34:22.494 --> 34:23.693
        That's my point.        

34:26.231 --> 34:28.732
           <i> Come on..</i>           

34:28.734 --> 34:30.367
          <i> They're not</i>          
       <i> all sad, are they?</i>      

34:30.369 --> 34:32.202
            The ones            
       I think about are.       

34:36.208 --> 34:38.141
        It won't always         
         be like that.          

34:40.746 --> 34:42.612
      <i> At least that's what</i>     
           <i> they say.</i>           

34:48.120 --> 34:50.520
          What's wrong          
        with your hand?         

34:50.522 --> 34:52.355
     This stupid splinter.      

34:58.230 --> 35:00.530
          <i> What are you</i>         
          <i> doing, bud?</i>          

35:00.532 --> 35:02.466
          Dad's knife           
         has tweezers.          

35:02.468 --> 35:03.467
      Okay. Let Jen do it.      

35:03.469 --> 35:04.868
            No, it..            

35:04.870 --> 35:06.603
           It's okay.           

35:09.141 --> 35:10.207
        This might sting        
           a little.            

35:10.209 --> 35:12.242
          [Jen groans]          

35:12.244 --> 35:14.211
          - I'm sorry.          
     - It's okay. Go ahead.     

35:16.782 --> 35:18.582
             There.             

35:18.584 --> 35:20.817
       Thank you, doctor.       

35:20.819 --> 35:23.553
            That was            
       very professional.       

35:23.555 --> 35:26.256
      Good bedside manner       
         is a lost art.         

35:26.258 --> 35:28.725
            [laughs]            
             What?              

35:28.727 --> 35:31.561
         Where the hell         
       did you hear that?       

35:31.563 --> 35:33.897
        <i> Grandpa wouldn't</i>       
       <i> shut up about it.</i>       

35:33.899 --> 35:35.632
            [laughs]            

35:36.668 --> 35:39.436
    He is such a gentleman.     

35:49.681 --> 35:51.781
    <i> I just.. I have no idea</i>    
      <i> what to say to him.</i>      

35:53.452 --> 35:56.720
         <i> Well, I think</i>         
         <i> that's normal.</i>        

35:56.722 --> 35:59.389
   <i> You guys are both hurting</i>   
        <i> and just dealing</i>       
      <i> with it differently.</i>     

35:59.391 --> 36:01.725
    I know, I just wish that    
     he would listen to me.     

36:06.532 --> 36:10.433
         Maybe you try          
      to include him more.      

36:10.435 --> 36:12.235
      Be honest with him.       

36:13.438 --> 36:16.439
        You don't think         
          I'm honest?           

36:16.441 --> 36:18.708
     You shelter him, Abs.      

36:18.710 --> 36:20.677
            He's 13.            

36:20.679 --> 36:22.479
       <i> He can handle it,</i>       
    <i> you can tell him stuff.</i>    

36:22.481 --> 36:24.281
         Where is this          
          coming from?          

36:25.884 --> 36:27.717
         <i> You asked for</i>         
           <i> my advice.</i>          

36:29.488 --> 36:31.288
         Mm, talk to me         
      about raising a kid       

36:31.290 --> 36:33.290
       when you have one.       

36:36.795 --> 36:39.262
    Well, I've been thinking    
      about having a baby.      

36:46.939 --> 36:49.806
     What? Are you serious?     

36:49.808 --> 36:51.608
           [laughing]           

36:55.247 --> 36:58.782
        Yeah, I've been         
       thinking about it.       

36:58.784 --> 37:00.250
     I just.. I didn't want     
         to mention it          

37:00.252 --> 37:01.918
       because that's not       
      why we're out here.       

37:01.920 --> 37:03.386
           [laughing]           

37:06.825 --> 37:08.792
         I mean, when?          

37:08.794 --> 37:09.926
     <i> Did you meet someone?</i>     

37:09.928 --> 37:11.561
             - No.              
            -<i> Wait!</i>             

37:11.563 --> 37:12.662
        <i> Are you getting</i>        
            <i> a donor?</i>           

37:12.664 --> 37:14.264
