37:14.266 --> 37:15.865
      <i> Relax, I still have</i>      

37:15.867 --> 37:18.268
      <i> to go to the doctor</i>      
         <i> and do tests.</i>         

37:20.339 --> 37:21.605
           You think            
       it's a good idea?        

37:21.607 --> 37:23.673
            <i> I think</i>            
       <i> it's a great idea.</i>      

37:23.675 --> 37:25.308
           - Really?            
             -<i> Yes.</i>             

37:25.310 --> 37:28.011
      I think you're gonna      
      make an amazing mom.      

37:28.013 --> 37:29.813
         <i> Look how good</i>         
       <i> you are with Sam!</i>       

37:29.815 --> 37:31.448
          <i> He actually</i>          
        <i> listens to you.</i>        

37:31.450 --> 37:33.016
        He's a teenager.        

37:33.018 --> 37:34.517
           They don't           
      come out like that.       

37:34.519 --> 37:35.919
        No, they don't.         

37:44.663 --> 37:45.929
       Michael and I were       
         talking about          

37:45.931 --> 37:48.031
      having another baby       
      before he got sick.       

37:57.576 --> 37:59.376
    This is gonna be better.    

38:00.545 --> 38:03.680
        Oh, I can change        
       the dirty diapers        

38:03.682 --> 38:05.448
       and you come over        
     and spoil him rotten.      

38:05.450 --> 38:06.583
              Yes.              

38:06.585 --> 38:07.651
            [laughs]            

38:08.720 --> 38:10.453
            Oh, Jen.            

38:11.323 --> 38:13.056
    Come here, I want a hug.    

38:13.058 --> 38:15.725
   - We'll see, I don't know.   
          - Come here!          

38:15.727 --> 38:16.793
            [laughs]            

38:16.795 --> 38:17.961
              Ahh!              

38:21.633 --> 38:23.600
        Well, you know,         
           we'll see.           

38:24.936 --> 38:27.404
           We'll see.           
           It just..            

38:27.406 --> 38:29.472
     It gives me something      
      to look forward to.       

38:30.642 --> 38:32.042
     You're gonna get fat!      

38:32.044 --> 38:34.077
     I'm gonna get so fat!      

38:34.079 --> 38:35.345
            Finally!            

38:35.347 --> 38:37.714
        [both laughing]         

38:41.553 --> 38:43.553
      [crickets chirping]       

38:44.356 --> 38:46.890
        [music on radio]        

