        <i> ¶ Could we make</i>        
         <i> another try? ¶</i>        

39:38.543 --> 39:40.744
           [whispers]           
              Jen.              

39:40.746 --> 39:43.146
       <i> ¶ If at first.. ¶</i>       

39:43.148 --> 39:45.548
           [whispers]           
              Jen.              

39:45.550 --> 39:47.784
         <i> ¶ Try again ¶</i>         

39:47.786 --> 39:50.019
         <i> ¶ Try again ¶</i>         

39:50.021 --> 39:51.721
           <i> ¶ Memory ¶</i>          

39:51.723 --> 39:52.856
           [whispers]           
              Jen.              

39:53.959 --> 39:57.694
      <i> ¶ And you love me ¶</i>      

39:57.696 --> 39:58.928
    <i> ¶ Say that it will.. ¶¶</i>    

39:58.930 --> 40:00.063
              Jen?              

40:03.402 --> 40:04.901
              Jen?              

