             - Jen?             
             -<i> Mom.</i>             

40:11.143 --> 40:13.109
           <i> Jen's not</i>           
      <i> in her tent, honey.</i>      

40:13.111 --> 40:14.911
     Maybe she had to pee.      

40:16.615 --> 40:17.947
              Jen!              

40:21.753 --> 40:23.019
              Jen!              

40:26.458 --> 40:28.458
        [intense music]         

40:35.534 --> 40:36.833
           Jennifer!            

40:38.170 --> 40:40.003
              Jen!              

40:44.676 --> 40:45.975
              <i> Jen!</i>             

40:49.014 --> 40:51.681
        <i> ¶ Another try ¶</i>        

40:51.683 --> 40:55.752
        <i> ¶ Could we make</i>        
         <i> another try? ¶</i>        

40:55.754 --> 40:58.188
              Jen!              

40:58.190 --> 40:59.656
              Jen!              

40:59.658 --> 41:02.158
              Jen!              

41:02.160 --> 41:03.960
              Jen!              

41:06.531 --> 41:07.530
              <i> Jen!</i>             

41:08.934 --> 41:10.567
              <i> Jen!</i>             

41:13.038 --> 41:16.539
           <i> ¶ Say that</i>          
       <i> it will never be ¶</i>      

41:17.742 --> 41:20.510
       <i> ¶ Just a memory ¶¶</i>      

41:20.512 --> 41:22.579
              <i> Jen!</i>             

41:22.581 --> 41:25.048
              <i> Jen!</i>             

41:26.585 --> 41:27.851
       [music continues]        

41:33.625 --> 41:35.058
             Jen..              

